B.P6=s(["High Precision: Calculates Moha Songkran (Khmer New Year) dates, times, and durations.","Leap Support: Automatically detects Leap Months (Athikameas) and Leap Days (Chantreathimeas).","Bilingual Out of the Box: Supports Khmer & English formatting and naming conventions.","Holy Day Detection: Helper methods for special Buddhist days like isSilaDay and isFullMoon."],t.s)
B.Rh=new A.bq(B.mc,["package_2","flutter_khmer_chankitec","A high-precision, zero-dependency Dart package for the Khmer Lunar Calendar (Chhankitek / \u1785\u1793\u17d2\u1791\u1782\u178f\u17b7). Performs astronomical calculations for lunar transitions, Khmer New Year determinations, and date conversions. Compiles directly to any target platform with zero overhead.","https://pub.dev/packages/flutter_khmer_chankitec","https://github.com/vengann/flutter_khmer_chankitec","1.0.2",B.P8,B.P6,"import 'package:flutter_khmer_chankitec/flutter_khmer_chankitec.dart';\n\n// Get current lunar date\nfinal lunarDate = Chhankitek.now();\n\nprint(lunarDate.toString());\n// Output: \u1790\u17d2\u1784\u17c3\u17a2\u17b6\u1791\u17b7\u178f\u17d2\u1799 \u17e1\u17e0 \u1780\u17be\u178f \u1781\u17c2\u1794\u17bb\u179f\u17d2\u179f \u1786\u17d2\u1793\u17b6\u17c6\u179a\u17c4\u1784...\n\nif (lunarDate.isSilaDay) {\n  print(\"Today is Sila day (\u1790\u17d2\u1784\u17c3\u179f\u17b8\u179b)!\");\n}"],t.R)
